Description:
LIVINGSTON ESTATE - 4 BEDROOM, 3 LIVING AREAS!! * CALL TODAY TO BOOK AN INSPECTION *
CRANBOURNE EAST - LIVINGSTON ESTATE - As you take a step into this beautiful 4 bedroom and 3 living area family home, you will be instantly impressed with the quality it has to offer. Suitable for all buyers and offering the perfect location close to parkland, amenities and more!
The functional floorplan offers plenty of space for the large family or growing family. Central kitchen offering stone bench tops, stainless steel appliances, gas cooking and rangehood all overlooking the family meals area. There is a separate family room as well as another living area which could be used as the perfect retreat for the kids to enjoy.
Outside you are greeted with the decked alfresco with the bonus of an outdoor spa and a low maintenance yard.
The spacious master bedroom has a walk in robe and ensuite with double sink basins. All three other bedrooms have built in robes and the main central bathroom with both bath and shower facilities.
Features include:
- Plantation shutters
- Floating timber floors
- Split system
- Outdoor spa
- Evaporative cooling
- Ducted heating
- Double lock up garage with internal access
- Security Cameras
- 20 Solar panels
Cranbourne East is located on the outskirts of Cranbourne Central. The area offers Cranbourne East Primary and Cranbourne East Secondary College as well as Cranbourne Secondary College and is surrounded by multiple Shopping Centres. Also located nearby is the newly constructed Casey Fields football ground, Casey Race Recreation & Aquatic Centre, and Casey Library.
At Ray White Cranbourne our price indications are based upon probable market value, the likely selling price and vendor expectations. You can view with confidence that vendors will sell within the range with favourable conditions.

5 Bed, 2 Bath, 2 Toilets, 3 Living, 2 Car Garage, Total under roof Area 33 sqm

• 5 bedrooms, master with walk-in robe, ensuite and bay window

Description:
Private oasis with two living areas
Located in the heart of the HUNT CLUB, one of the most sort after estates of Cranbourne East is this beautiful family home positioned on a quiet established street. Ideal for first home buyers and investors alike, you will love the spacious living zones and beautiful private gardens on offer here.
Comprising of:
Three spacious bedrooms, master with large en-suite and walk in robe, whilst the remaining 2 bedrooms both have built in robes.
The hostess kitchen includes a dishwasher, island bench with breakfast bar and quality appliances. It's well positioned and has an open and inviting feel whilst overlooking the dining area.
Two separate living areas provide enough room for both parents and kids, with a spacious front formal lounge / theater room and an open plan family area at the rear with access to the alfresco.
The large alfresco area is ideal to enjoy a BBQ with friends and family all year round plus the spacious backyard offers plenty of room for kids and pets to play.
Added extras include; ducted heating, evaporative cooling, color bond fencing, ornament recesses to the hall way and a double remote garage with internal access.
A fantastic location is also on offer with a park just around the corner, as well as bus stops and walking/bicycle paths nearby. Childcare facilities, primary and secondary schools and the Hunt Club Village Shopping Center are also only a stone throw away.
What are you waiting for? This one ticks all the boxes so don't miss out!
Features:
- Master with full ensuite & WIR.
- 2 Large separate living areas.
- Kitchen with quality appliances.
- Large all-weather alfresco area overlooking backyard.
- Heating and cooling plus plenty of extras.

The unique industrial style kitchen has ample bench and cupboard space, stone benches, dishwasher and quality appliances. It's centrally positioned and has an open and inviting feel, overlooking the huge separate dining area, perfect for hosting dinner with the fam!
The two separate living areas provide enough room for both parents and kids, with a spacious front formal lounge or theater room and an informal family area at the rear with access to the huge alfresco. Outside you'll find lush, manicured gardens back and front.
The decked alfresco area is ideal to enjoy with friends and family all year round - it features a beautiful fish pond and high pitched roof. You'll also find a fenced undercover spa to kick back and relax in after a long day as well a decent sized backyard for the kids and pets to play.
Added extras include; ducted heating, evaporative cooling, split system A/C, feature walls, garden shed, secure SIDE ACCESS to store a trailer or car and double remote garage with internal access.
A fantastic location within seconds walk to the Hunt Club shopping village, Wetlands, walking/bicycle paths, childcare, primary and secondary schools and public transport.
Features:
- Master with full ensuite & WIR.
- 2 Large separate living areas.
- Large decked alfresco area overlooking backyard and spa.
- Side access parking and double garage.
- Heating and cooling plus much more.
This home is perfect if you're looking for more space for your family. Don't miss out.
